aa.svg|100px|border]] || 1939<ref>https://dea.digar.ee/cgi-bin/dea?a=d&d=AKriigiteataja19390815.2.4</ref>\u20131940 || [[Petseri County]] ||\n|}\n\n== Historical flags ==\n\n=== [[Kingdom of Denmark|Denmark]] (1219\u20131346 and 1559\u20131645) ===\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-  bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! width=\"110\"|Flag!!width=\"100\"|Date!!width=\"250\"|Use!!width=\"250\"|Description\n|-\n| [[File:Flag of Denmark.svg|100px|border]] || 1219\u20131346<br/>1559\u20131645  || [[Flag of Denmark]] ||\n|}\n\n=== [[Livonian Order|Livonia]] (1237\u20131561) ===\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-  bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! width=\"110\"|Flag!!width=\"100\"|Date!!width=\"250\"|Use!!width=\"250\"|Description\n|-\n| [[File:Flag of the Teutonic Order.svg|100px]] || 1237\u20131561  || Flag of the State of the Teutonic Order ||\n|}\n\n=== [[Kingdom of Sweden|Sweden]] (1561\u20131721) ===\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-  bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! width=\"110\"|Flag!!width=\"100\"|Date!!width=\"250\"|Use!!width=\"250\"|Description\n|-\n| [[File:Sweden-Flag-1562.svg|100px]] || 1561-ca. 1650 || [[Flag of Sweden]] ||\n|-\n| [[File:Naval Ensign of Sweden.svg|100px]] || ca. 1650-<br/>1710/1721 || Flag of Sweden ||\n|}\n\n=== [[Grand Duchy of Lithuania|Lithuania]] (1561\u20131569) ===\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-  bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! width=\"110\"|Flag!!width=\"100\"|Date!!width=\"250\"|Use!!width=\"250\"|Description\n|-\n| [[File:Alex K Grundwald flags 1410-03.svg|100px]] || 156