0\"|Date!!width=\"250\"|Use!!width=\"250\"|Description\n|-\n| [[File:Flag of Estonia.svg|100px|border]] || 1918\u20131940<br/>1944 <br />1988/1990\u2013present|| State flag and civil ensign || Dimensions are 7:11; colors were standardized in 2014.\n|}\n\n== Governmental flags ==\n\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-  bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! width=\"110\"|Flag!!width=\"100\"|Date!!width=\"250\"|Use!!width=\"250\"|Description\n|-\n| [[File:Flag of the President of Estonia.svg|100px|border]] || 1992\u2013present <br/> 1927<ref>http://www.ra.ee/dgs/_purl.php?shc=ERA.31.2.1041a:64</ref>-1940 ||Presidential standard||National tricolour with the greater coat of arms in the center\n|-\n| [[File:Presidential Standard of Estonia (at sea).svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present ||Presidential standard (at sea)||Swallow-tailed tricolour with the greater coat of arms in the center\n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Minister of Defence.svg|100px|border]] || ?\u2013present ||Defence Minister||National tricolour with the lesser coat of arms off-set to hoist \n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Postal Flag.svg|100px|border]] || ?\u2013present || Postal flag ||\n\n|}\n\n== Military flags ==\n\n{| border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse;\"\n|-  bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! width=\"110\"|Flag!!width=\"100\"|Date!!width=\"250\"|Use!!width=\"250\"|Description\n|-\n| [[File:Naval Ensign of Estonia.svg|100px]] || 1991\u2013present <br/> 1926\u20131940 || Naval ensign || Swallow-tailed  tricolour with the lesser coat of arms in the center \n|-\n| [[File:Naval Jack of Estonia.svg|border|100px]] || 1991\u2013present <br/> 1926\u20131940 || Naval jack ||Dimension: 7:11 (the saltaire equals 1 part, the George's cross 2 parts)\n|-\n| [[File:State Flag of the Estonian Air Force (obverse).png|100px]] || ?\u2013present || State flag of the Estonian Air Force ||\n|-\n| [[File:Kvyldlipp.jpg|100px]] || rowspan=2|2008\u2013present || rowspan=2|Flag of the Estonian Defense Forces ||rowspan=2|\n|-\n| [[File:Kvyldlipp.svg|100px|border]]\n|-\n| [[File:Flag of the Estonian Land Forces.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Flag of the Estonian Land Forces ||\n|-\n| [[File:Flag of the Estonian Air Force (reverse).png|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Flag of the Estonian Air Force ||\n|-\n| [[File:Kaitseliit flag - obverse.jpg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Flag of the Defence League (obverse) ||\n|-\n| [[File:Kaitseliit flag - reverse.jpg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Flag of the Defence League (reverse) ||\n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Chief of Naval Forces.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Chief of Naval Forces ||White triangular swallow tailed pennant (broad pennant) with blue \"chevron\" rising from the hoist and with yellow anchor near the hoist\n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Rear Admiral.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Rear admiral\u2019s Flag ||Flag similar to CinC Armed Forces but without any yellow borders\n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Lieutenant General.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Lieutenant general\u2019s Flag ||Flag similar to CinC Armed Forces but with yellow edge only at the top\n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Major General.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Major general\u2019s flag ||Flag similar to CinC Armed Forces but with yellow edge only along the lower edge\n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Chief of Division.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Chief of division || The same flag as Chief of Naval Forces, but without the anchor\n|-\n| [[File:Flags of Estonia - Senior Officer Afloat.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || Senior Officer Afloat ||White triangular pennant with horizontal blue stripe though the middle\n|-\n| [[File:Flag of None.svg|100px]] || ?\u2013present || General Agent of the Navy||National flag with two crossed anchors in the top c